data.description: What a find in the Hoover/Vestavia Area. This will make a great property for anyone. Living/Dining Area with a huge ceiling fan. Nice sized bedrooms and closet space.  Full Bath in the hallway.  Check out the Sunroom at the back and the large storage building.  Yard is great for kids and fenced.  Much more and a must see.  All offers must have proof of funds with the offer. Showings by appointment only.  This home will not last long.
